data.description: This beautiful home is waiting for its new owners! Located in The Oaks of Fowl River subdivision, this home offers 4 bedrooms -3.5 bathrooms, and Approx. 2682 sq ft! Large open concept living and kitchen area, with eat in breakfast area and separate dining room. Beautiful crown molding, whole house built in vacuum system, and grand 10ft+ ceilings.  Split floor plan with Primary bedroom and laundry room on one side. Primary bedroom has a large en suite bathroom with separate walk-in closets. One of the walk-in closets opens to the laundry room for easy access. On the other side of the house are the three remaining bedrooms. One of the spare bedrooms and primary bedroom have updated LVP flooring. The large back porch has an attached bathroom with a shower. Also, on the back porch is a large kitchen area with a Green Egg Grill which is great for entertaining! Very spacious back yard with plenty of space. PER SELLER NO HOA. Don’t miss this one! Call your favorite agent and go check it out! ALL UPDATED ARE PER THE SELLERS: Roof-2021(Fortified), Septic last pumped- June 2022, Two AC Units less than 5 years old, water heater between 3-4 years old, front flower bed retaining wall redone in the last 3-4 years. (LISTING AGENT MAKES NO REPRESENTATION TO ACCURACY OF LOT DIMENSIONS OR SQUARE FOOTAGE. BUYER TO VERIFY. ANY AND ALL UPDATES ARE PER SELLER(S).
